DataElement.preferredName: Notification Performed Study Activity Actual Date and Time Range ISO21090.IVL.TS.DATETIME.v1.0
DataElement.preferredDefinition: The completed activity within the context of a given study that represents the communication of a message to a recipient. The date and time span when this activity began and ended. EXAMPLE(S): The date and time when a sample is taken from the subject. A dose of chemotherapy is given on June 12th starting at 9am and finishing at 12pm.
